---
// Arquitetura do soapbar: cliente e servidor sobre um core compartilhado.
interface Props {
  lang?: 'pt' | 'en';
}
const { lang = 'pt' } = Astro.props;

const t = {
  pt: {
    server: 'Servidor',
    client: 'Cliente',
    envelope: '▼ envelope SOAP 1.1 / 1.2',
    dispatch: 'dispatch · WS-Security · WS-Addressing · limites anti-DoS',
    core: 'core compartilhado',
    caption:
      'Os cinco estilos de binding, a segurança e o parsing vivem num único core: o mesmo que atende cliente e servidor. Os clientes de domínio (contrib) são casca fina sobre ele.',
  },
  en: {
    server: 'Server',
    client: 'Client',
    envelope: '▼ SOAP 1.1 / 1.2 envelope',
    dispatch: 'dispatch · WS-Security · WS-Addressing · anti-DoS limits',
    core: 'shared core',
    caption:
      'The five binding styles, security, and parsing all live in a single core: the same one that serves client and server. The domain (contrib) clients are a thin shell on top of it.',
  },
}[lang];

const core = ['binding', 'envelope', 'types', 'wsdl', 'xml', 'fault'];
const box = 'rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg px-4 py-2.5 text-center';
const arrow = 'flex flex-col items-center py-1 text-muted';
---

<figure class="not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-lg flex-col items-stretch text-sm">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
      <div class={box}>
        <div class="font-medium text-fg">{t.server}</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-muted">AsgiSoapApp · WsgiSoapApp</div>
      </div>
      <div class={box}>
        <div class="font-medium text-fg">{t.client}</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-muted">SoapClient · contrib (VIES · WITSML · NF-e)</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class={arrow} aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="h-3 w-px bg-border"></div>
      <span class="text-[10px] leading-none">{t.envelope}</span>
    </div>

    <div class={box}>
      <span class="font-medium text-fg">SoapApplication</span>
      <p class="mt-0.5 text-xs text-muted">{t.dispatch}</p>
    </div>

    <div class={arrow} aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="h-3 w-px bg-border"></div>
      <span class="text-[10px] leading-none">▼</span>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-lg border border-accent/40 bg-bg px-4 py-3">
      <div class="text-center text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-accent">{t.core}</div>
      <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-1.5">
        {core.map((m) => <span class="badge border-border font-mono text-xs text-muted">{m}</span>)}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <figcaption class="mt-4 text-center text-xs text-muted">{t.caption}</figcaption>
</figure>
